text: Odem High School is a public high school located in the city of Odem, Texas, in San Patricio County, United States and classified as a 3A school by the UIL. It is a part of the Odem Independent School District located in east central San Patricio County. In 2015, the school was rated "Met Standard" by the Texas Education Agency. ==References== Category:Public high schools in Texas Category:Schools in San Patricio County, Texas Category:Corpus Christi metropolitan area
